title: Seahawks Have Yet To Name Starting QB
description:
Pete Carroll weighs in on the ongoing QB battle in Seattle, Tua Tagovailoa is confident in the Dolphins offense, we hear from Ryan Clark after his sitdown interview with Davante Adams, Sammy Watkins compares Aaron Rodgers and Patrick Mahomes and our thoughts on the Cowboys for the upcoming season.
